$(document).ready(function(){$(".details").click(function(){var l=$(this).attr("value");$.get("/student/events/"+l,function(l){if("Deleted"==l)refresh();else{var e="<div class='row'><div class='col-md-6'><div class='form-group'><label>Event Name:</label><br>"+l.title+"</div></div><div class='col-md-6'><div class='form-group'><label>Event Place:</label><br>"+l.place_held+"</div></div><div class='col-md-12'><div class='form-group'><label>Event Date:</label><br>"+l.date+"</div></div><div class='col-md-6'><div class='form-group'><label>From:</label><br>"+l.time_f+"</div></div><div class='col-md-6'><div class='form-group'><label>To:</label><br>"+l.time_t+"</div></div><div class='col-md-12'><div class='form-group'><label>Description:</label><br>"+l.description+"</div></div></div>";bootbox.alert({title:"View Event",message:e,backdrop:!0,buttons:{ok:{label:"Ok",className:"btn-success btn-md"}}})}})})});